 the United States.svg|border|centre|100px|link=Flag of the United States|alt=Flag the United States]]\n| [[File:United States on the globe (North America centered).svg|centre|150px|alt=Map showing the United States in an orthographic projection]]\n| [[United States]]\n| [[Washington, D.C.]]\n| {{dts|24 August 1949}}{{efn|name=found}}\n| 332,639,102\n| {{sort|3531905|{{convert|9833520|km2|sqmi|0|abbr=on}}}}\n|}\n\n==Military personnel==\nThe following list is sourced from the 2018 edition of \"The Military Balance\" published annually by the [[International Institute for Strategic Studies]].\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:left;\"\n|-\n! data-sort-type = \"number\" |\n! Country\n! data-sort-type = \"number\" |Active military\n! data-sort-type = \"number\" |Reserve military\n! data-sort-type = \"number\" |Paramilitary\n! data-sort-type = \"number\" |Total\n! data-sort-type = \"number\" |Per 1000 capita<br>(total)\n! data-sort-type = \"number\" |Per 1000 capita<br>(active)\n{{Number of soldiers| country=Albania| military=Military of Albania| active=8000| reserve=0| paramilitary=500| population=3047987|references=<ref>[[#IISS2018|IISS 2018]], pp. 82</ref>}}\n{{Number of soldiers| country=Belgium| military=Belgian Armed Forces| active=28800| reserve=5000| paramilitary=0| population=11491346| references=<ref>[[#IISS2018|IISS 2018]], pp. 85</ref>}}\n{{Number of soldiers| country=Bulgaria| military=Military of Bulgaria| active=31300| reserve=3000| paramilitary=0| population=7101510| references=<ref>[[#IISS2018|IISS 2018]], pp. 88</ref>}}\n{{Number of soldiers| country=Canada| military=Canadian Forces| active=63000| reserve=30000| paramilitary=4500| population=35623680| references=<ref>[[#IISS2018|IISS 2018]], pp. 43</ref>}}\n{{Number of soldiers| country=Croatia| military=Military of Croatia| active=15650| reserve=0| paramilitary=3000| population=4292095| references=<ref>[[#IISS2018|IISS 2018]], pp. 90</ref>}}\n{{Number of soldiers| country=Czechia| mili